OL,3,CThe Spring Index: How you can help
OL,4,Cnature this spring
OL,6,FAfter a long, soggy winter, spring is
OL,7,Ffinally here and the sights and sounds
OL,8,Fare arriving by the day.
OL,10,FFor the Woodland Trust it's all about
OL,11,Fthe 'Spring Index', indicating how the
OL,12,Fnatural world is reacting to our
OL,13,Fchanging climate.
OL,15,FIt's all part of a wider, long-running
OL,16,Fproject known as Nature's Calendar and
OL,17,Fthe good news is that we can all take
OL,18,Fpart.
OL,20,FYou can find out more and record your
OL,21,Fsightings here.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
