OL,3,CThe Spring Index: How you can help
OL,4,Cnature this spring
OL,6,FThe Spring Index looks at four main
OL,7,Findicators:
OL,9,FFirst flowering of hawthorn
OL,11,FFirst flowering of horse chestnut
OL,13,FFirst recorded flight of an orange
OL,14,Ftipped butterfly
OL,16,FFirst sighting of a swallow
OL,18,FWhy should I get involved?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
