OL,3,CThe Spring Index: How you can help
OL,4,Cnature this spring
OL,6,FStudies show that when we compare the
OL,7,Flast 25 years to the early part of the
OL,8,Flast century, these signs of spring
OL,9,Fare now arriving around 9 days
OL,10,Fearlier, in large part due to
OL,11,Fincreasing warmth during the months of
OL,12,FMarch and April.
OL,14,FThis causes a lot of confusion in the
OL,15,Fnatural world with pollinators out of
OL,16,Fsync with the plants they rely on,
OL,17,Fcompetition for food between species
OL,18,Fand subsequently serious consequences
OL,19,Ffor whole ecosystems.
OL,21,FAnd the good news?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
